{"tid":1130781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國駐英大使警告英國：不要歧視華為參與5G建設","createTime":"2019-04-29T09:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T00:49:24.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0ef589535ba50c56b82cf604265c7864e203eaab","tid":1130781,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T09:25:44.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕英國國家安全委員會（NSC）決定禁止華為參與英國5G網絡所有核心部分，並限制其在非核心部分的參與程度，中國駐英大使週日警告英國，不要歧視參與5G網路建設的企業，並敦促其應該與華為在合作的問題上，抵制其他國家的壓力。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》報導，中國駐英國大使劉曉明在英國星期日電訊報發表文章稱，<span style=\"color: red;\">華為始終保持良好安全記錄</span>，英國應該&ldquo;根據本國利益自主做出決定&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n他進一步指出，世界最不需要的就是對參與5G網絡建設的企業採取任何形式的歧視性舉措。中國最不希望從1個真正開放且公平的&ldquo;全球化英國&rdquo;看到的卻是不公平的競爭環境。<br />\n<br />\n他說，應該認真對待相關風險，但不應讓風險煽動恐懼，只要國家和企業共同努力，風險是可控的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2773579\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2773579&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9UYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=530e7bfc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2773579&h=91cb7138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2773579</a><br />\n<br />\n良好記錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60cc84fe766414a7de7df36a4cf8ffef4e38f738","tid":1130781,"uid":4285,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T09:27:35.000Z","msg":"警告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你警告我又唔撚驚"},{"pid":"dcff18233e167851a60f0b24240f714334747026","tid":1130781,"uid":164050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T09:29:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe540aad4fc2876c761389892596e56638ce933f","tid":1130781,"uid":39628,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T09:30:07.000Z","msg":"又係到干預別國事務<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85fd2c0e73fb5332c88d75ecb3f638cbdc59aa8c","tid":1130781,"uid":6752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T09:37:50.000Z","msg":"點解中國要出聲,又話唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"759f95738cf13505669253d58e06eed70ca96fa6","tid":1130781,"uid":125193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T09:40:22.000Z","msg":"中國駐英大使<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我記得2年前釣魚台單野日日同日本大使係網站，報紙post 文互屌<br />\n1年後習帝話中日友好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後條友即刻消失左<br />\n<br />\n之後日本大使最 post 暗吋中國紙老虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 釣魚島繼續係日方控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da0158b6be1cf244cfba2e2dd8d3b60efd75d6b2","tid":1130781,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T14:41:25.000Z","msg":"開始發爛渣"},{"pid":"1301f2ac5499e521103913f6b1f5d1c3d279de60","tid":1130781,"uid":227172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T17:07:01.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啦，走囉，杯葛囉，最撚識呢d架啦。"},{"pid":"ee8167f8c58c5972204764468a96c81bb24f3236","tid":1130781,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85fd2c0e73fb5332c88d75ecb3f638cbdc59aa8c","tid":1130781,"uid":6752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T09:37:50.000Z","msg":"點解中國要出聲,又話唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T17:08:11.000Z","msg":"國企露出尾巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98caf14b601eeb4e96c305848ddc4690810874f5","tid":1130781,"uid":137480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T23:54:28.000Z","msg":"英國佬比你建設5G又如何,拉條CABLE線都叫做建設5G呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞發射站就一定沒你份"},{"pid":"e4160f223df55c83c08a138910e16b9e8776bd69","tid":1130781,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:48:13.000Z","msg":"個政府幫間民企係咁講野<br />\n又唔幫下我間公司講野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb5d3a92c6c98755c854b6e4aaa726c682d0d4a","tid":1130781,"uid":34334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:49:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}